; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Mrs Madeleine Moon","Bridgend","Mrs Madeleine Moon","8818"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/416460","Home Office","false","2015-09-10","<p>Home Office staff consider Tier 2, 4 and 5 sponsor licence applications. The number of staff working on applications for a Tier 4 sponsor licence varies according to level of demand and resource requirements. We do not record the number of staff working on Tier 4 casework, specifically.</p>","Old Bexley and Sidcup","James Brokenshire",,"2015-09-10T14:01:38.76Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/416460/answer","Biography information for James Brokenshire","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/416460/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/416460/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2015-09-04","Home Office: Staff","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, pursuant to the Answer of 10 August 2015 to Question 4785 on education institutions: licensing, how many staff were working on applications for a Tier 4 sponsor licence in each year since 2008; and if she will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Mrs Madeleine Moon","Bridgend","Mrs Madeleine Moon","8836"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/416461","Home Office","false","2015-09-10","<p>All applications submitted during the year 2010 to 2013 have been concluded. There were 12 applications submitted during 2014, and 52 applications submitted during 2015 which are yet to be determined.</p>","Old Bexley and Sidcup","James Brokenshire",,"2015-09-10T14:01:22.403Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/416461/answer","Biography information for James Brokenshire","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/416461/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/416461/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2015-09-04","Overseas Students: Visas","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, pursuant to the Answer of 10 August 2015 to Question 4785 on education institutions: licensing, how many applications for a Tier 4 sponsor licence made in each year since 2010 are still undetermined; and if she will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Mrs Madeleine Moon","Bridgend","Mrs Madeleine Moon","8835"
